thread.title: Google to start overriding call extension numbers with location-specific phone numbers in ads

author: Ginny Marvin
title: Google to start overriding call extension numbers with location-specific phone numbers in ads
text:
Advertisers that depend on calls going to a central phone number for conversion tracking and other reasons will face a challenge as of January 19, 2017. The post Google to start overriding call extension numbers with location-specific phone numbers in ads appeared first on Search Engine Land.

Please visit Search Engine Land for the full article.
